| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-1656 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 53acd7c6-6952-5a68-991c-732e1f6ce5fd"
